Collection and Consent
To the extent required by applicable law, we will obtain your consent (separately, if applicable) to collect, use, share, transmit (including but not limited to overseas transmission), disclose or otherwise process your personal information.
Directly from You: We collect your information:
For sign up as a member of MeliáRewards programme, information collected include:
Nationality, name, surname, e-mail address, country of residence, phone number, date of birth
In order to provide a secure access to Melia Rewards, we will collect username and password.
Members’ data will be processed to manage registration in the Programme and for earning and redeeming points therefore one you become a member we will process all the data related to your
accommodation records
, and related to the earning and redeeming points. Such information is not collected when you register but is then processed when you are a member.
For book a stay, information collected include:
Gender, Nationality, name, surname, e-mail address, country of residence, phone number,
card data or other payment data
