To personalize the user experience and improve engagement by delivering customized content and features to users based on their behavior and preferences
Information Collected via SDK:
Device information:
- Device type
- Operating system
- Device language
- IP address
User behavior data:
- usage patterns
- clicks
- user interactions with the app
Sensitive Permission Requested:
N/A
